The Spinnaker device adapter was created by [https://www.cairn-research.co.uk CAIRN].   

== Installation ==
Download and install the [https://www.cairn-research.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/SpinnakerSDK_FULL_1.20.0.15_x64.exe Spinnaker driver from the CAIRN website].  Follow the instructions in this [https://www.cairn-research.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/READ-ME-INSTALLATION.pdf pdf on the CAIRN website].  Note that it is not needed to download 2.0-beta3-20181129, newer versions of Micro-Manager (1.4 and 2.0) should work as well.


